# Optional: Telegram Notifications
# If you want to receive signals on your phone via Telegram:
# 1. Talk to @BotFather on Telegram to create a bot and get the Token.
# 2. Talk to @userinfobot to get your Chat ID.
# 3. Fill them in here and rename this file from .env.example to .env

TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=your_telegram_bot_token_here
TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=your_telegram_chat_id_here